Date: Sun, 20 Jul 2025 21:24:40 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 9/9] QSDK: DP: wifi: ath12k: add memory stats for monitor
 destination ring

Add support to track the number of skbs and frags allocated/freed/deliver
to mac80211 for the monitor destination ring and monitor buffer ring.

device mon specific stats:
*******************radio[0]*****************
status frags reap: 1158 process: 1157 free: 1157
packet frags process 3113 free 0 to_mac80211 3113
Ring desc empty: 0 flush 0 truncated 0 droptlv 0
skb alloc: 3041 free: 0 to_mac80211: 3041
raw mode skb: 3041 frag 3113 eth mode skb: 0 frag:0
PPDU reaped 880 processed 880
frags replenished_cnt: 12276 used cnt 4270 tot_free_frags 4270

Frags hold by HW: 8005

Frags hold by SW: 1

SKBs hold by SW: 0

Patch-dependency:
0475-08-Upstream-DP-Add-logic-for-PPDU-based-reaping-for-mon.patch

Signed-off-by: P Praneesh <ppranees@qti.qualcomm.com>
